#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:1
msgid "PostgreSQL Deployment"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:3
msgid ""
"The LDE backend requires a dedicated PostgreSQL Flexible Server for each "
"environment. This is separate from the RONL Business API's `ronl-postgres-"
"prod` instance — see [Infrastructure decisions]{1} for the rationale."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:7
msgid "Provisioning"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:9
msgid "1 — Create the Flexible Server"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:11
msgid "Create one server per environment in the Azure Portal or via CLI:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:13
msgid "ACC: resource group `RONL-Preproduction`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:14
msgid "PROD: resource group `RONL-Production`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:16
msgid "Recommended tier: Burstable, 1–2 vCores."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:18
msgid "2 — Create the database and user"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:20
msgid "Connect to the new server as the admin user and run:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:21
msgid ""
"CREATE USER lde_user WITH PASSWORD '<strong-password>';\n"
"CREATE DATABASE lde_assets OWNER lde_user;\n"
"GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE lde_assets TO lde_user;\n"
"GRANT ALL ON SCHEMA public TO lde_user;\n"
"GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public TO lde_user;\n"
"ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES IN SCHEMA public GRANT ALL ON TABLES TO lde_user;"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:30
msgid ""
"!!! warning \"PostgreSQL 15+ public schema permissions\" Azure PostgreSQL "
"Flexible Server running PostgreSQL 15 or later revokes `CREATE` on the "
"`public` schema from non-superusers by default. The `GRANT ALL ON SCHEMA "
"public` statement is required — without it, the migration fails with "
"`permission denied for schema public` and the backend crashes on startup."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:33
msgid "3 — Configure App Settings"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:34
msgid ""
"az webapp config appsettings set \\\n"
"  --name ronl-linkeddata-backend-acc \\\n"
"  --resource-group RONL-Preproduction \\\n"
"  --settings \\\n"
"    DATABASE_URL=\"postgresql://lde_user:<password>@lde-postgres-"
"acc.postgres.database.azure.com:5432/lde_assets?sslmode=require\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:42
msgid ""
"az webapp config appsettings set \\\n"
"  --name ronl-linkeddata-backend-prod \\\n"
"  --resource-group RONL-Production \\\n"
"  --settings \\\n"
"    DATABASE_URL=\"postgresql://lde_user:<password>@lde-postgres-"
"prod.postgres.database.azure.com:5432/lde_assets?sslmode=require\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:50
msgid ""
"`sslmode=require` is mandatory — Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server enforces "
"SSL."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:52
msgid "4 — Deploy and verify"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:54
msgid ""
"Push to the `acc` branch. The CI/CD pipeline builds and deploys the backend. "
"On first startup `migrate()` creates all three tables automatically."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:56
msgid "Check the App Service log stream for:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:57
msgid ""
"[DB] Migrations applied\n"
"Server started"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:62
msgid "Then smoke-test the asset endpoints:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:63
msgid ""
"curl https://acc.backend.linkeddata.open-regels.nl/v1/assets/bpmn\n"
"curl https://acc.backend.linkeddata.open-regels.nl/v1/assets/forms\n"
"curl https://acc.backend.linkeddata.open-regels.nl/v1/assets/documents"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:69
msgid "All three should return `{\"success\":true,\"data\":[]}`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:73
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:75
msgid "`permission denied for schema public`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:77
msgid "**Symptom:** Backend crashes on startup with:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:78
msgid ""
"error: permission denied for schema public\n"
"code: '42501'"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:83
msgid ""
"**Cause:** Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server (PostgreSQL 15+) does not grant "
"`CREATE` on the `public` schema to non-superusers by default."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:85
msgid "**Fix:** Connect as the admin user to `lde_assets` and run:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:86
msgid ""
"GRANT ALL ON SCHEMA public TO lde_user;\n"
"GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public TO lde_user;\n"
"ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES IN SCHEMA public GRANT ALL ON TABLES TO lde_user;"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:92
msgid "The third statement covers future tables created by migrations."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:94
msgid "To find the server name:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:95
msgid ""
"az postgres flexible-server list \\\n"
"  --resource-group RONL-Preproduction \\\n"
"  --query \"[].{name:name, host:fullyQualifiedDomainName}\" \\\n"
"  --output table"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:104
msgid "SSL warning on startup"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:106
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\developer\\deployment-postgresql.md:106"
