msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:124
msgid "[DB] Skipping migrations — database not configured"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:128
msgid ""
"The backend starts successfully but all `/v1/assets/*` endpoints return `503 "
"DB_NOT_CONFIGURED`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:130
msgid ""
"**Fix:** Add `DATABASE_URL` to the App Service Application Settings. The App "
