msgid "**Symptom:** CI/CD health check step reports HTTP 503 after deployment."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:138
msgid ""
"**Most likely cause:** The backend is crashing on startup — `migrate()` is "
